00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:02.239
Yansheng.

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:02.840
Yansheng.

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:03.239
Mamá…

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:03.959
Yansheng!

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:04.560
¡Mamá!

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:05.959
¡Gu Chen Yu!

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:07.640
¡La familia Gu será mía!

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.520
